        @Nullable
Object evaluate(Formula f)
        Evaluate a given formula substituting the values from the model. Can be absent if the value is not relevant to the satisfiability result.
        Parameters:
        f - Input formula
        Returns:
        Either of: - Number (Rational/Double/BigInteger/Long/Integer) - Boolean
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if a formula has unexpected type, e.g Array.
